<div class="com-share" data-id="13360" data-title="《梅姨新片出演摇滚乐手，表演惊艳但电影比较一般》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13360/medium/13360.jpg?1439278323" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13360.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
